combination. Now Dividend Miles'' members can redeem miles
for travel on American Airlines and Advantage® members
can redeem miles for travel on US Airways. Members of both
programs can also combine miles from each program to claim
a travel award. When you're ready to redeem or combine your
miles for a travel award ticket, call American Airlines
at 1-800-882-8880 or US Airways at 1-800-428-4322
(for international travel, call 1-800-622-1015).
To combine miles, provide your account numbers and the
number of miles you wish to combine from each travel awards
program (minimum 1,000 miles from each program; 21-day
advance booking required). It's a win, win situation for you.
